text: Sean Foley may refer to: *Seán Foley (born 1949), Irish sportsman *Sean Foley (director) (born 1964), British theatre director, actor and writer *Sean Foley (golf instructor) (born 1974), Canadian golf instructor who coaches several PGA Tour players *Sean Foley (ethnographer), Irish ethnographer *Sean Foley (film editor), American film editor, whose credits include The Slumber Party Massacre *Sean Foley, American musician of Bright Eyes ==See also== *Sean Reid-Foley (born 1995), American baseball player *Shaun Foley (born 1986), Australian rugby league footballer
title: Sean Foley
